&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Design Engineer focused on Electronics, you will create innovative concepts for the mechanical integration of electronic boards, connectors, and harnesses, ensuring their proper form, fit, and function. Your expertise will be vital in realising robust, scalable, and cost-effective solutions that enhance the performance of Helsing&#39;s systems, directly supporting our mission to provide advanced defence capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
