&lt;li&gt;Perform circuit simulation and analysis&amp;nbsp;using tools such as&amp;nbsp;LTSpice&amp;nbsp;to validate design decisions early in the development cycle&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to reliability and safety analyses, including&amp;nbsp;FMEA&amp;nbsp;and reliability prediction, to ensure designs meet required standards&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
