&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;11084&quot;&gt;As a Field Engineer at Helsing, you will play a crucial role in maturing Helsing&#39;s cutting-edge military AI products from proof-of-concept to large-scale rollout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;11251&quot;&gt;You will be testing combined software and hardware products throughout the product development lifecycle in collaboration with world-class software and AI engineers, product managers, and end users as part of a tight iteration loop. You will ultimately help to assure Helsing’s products, to demonstrate that they are safe and reliable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;You’ll-do-great-if-you….3&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;15247&quot;&gt;The day-to-day&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Testing combined software and hardware products end-to-end in the lab and in the field (including flying drones), capturing data, and providing feedback to Helsing’s software and AI engineers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Packing equipment, transporting it to the test locations (e.g., airfields), setting it up, performing tests, and then packing up at the end of the day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Installing AI software onto edge computing devices, using Helsing&#39;s in-house deployment tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Helping to design and improve test plans and safety SOPs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Defining and securing the resources we need to maintain an effective and efficient field testing operation, and helping to secure them. For example, this may include purchasing hardware, trialling new software tools for inventory management and QA, establishing new secure storage facilities, and preparing safety cases and submissions to aviation authorities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Advising on training course design and in-service support procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Travel to other testing locations in the UK, France, Germany, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
