&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a regression test library spanning CAN/DroneCAN protocol behaviour, interface timing, and power profiles, producing formal clearance reports that gate each hardware and firmware revision before integration proceeds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
