&lt;li&gt;Are proficient in industry-standard CFD and thermal analysis tools such as ANSYS Fluent, Star-CCM+, Siemens Simcenter or OpenFOAM, and can apply these to both steady-state and transient flow regimes&lt;/li&gt;
